<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Wilhelm III. von Wittelsbach, Herzog von Bayern-München</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Hans Erlbeck, Diener der Stadt, wegen Werner Neumeyr an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_609" id="303v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_609_r1l1">Hercʒog <expan>wılhelm<ex>m</ex></expan> von Peyern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_609_r1l2"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> als vns eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> nehſt <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_609_r1l3"><expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> haben . als von des <expan>wernh<ex>er</ex></expan> Neẅmeyrs <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_609_r1l4">etc / Alſo <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> wır ʒu <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Erlpek<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_609_r1l5"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> . dem wır befolhen haben . <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu ercʒeln </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_609_r1l6">wıe ſıch <expan>dıeſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ſache <expan>ergang<ex>en</ex></expan> haben Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_609_r1l7">fleıſʒ / was <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> in <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ſachen ʒu dıſem mal von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_609_r1l9"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an eẅr gnade werbe / Daʒ Jr Jn 
<add><ab facs="#facs_609_r1l8">vmb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> darinn <expan>gnedıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_609_r1l10"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> . Jm des <expan>gencʒl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gelawben . vnd <expan>günſtıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_609_r1l11"><expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> darumb <expan>fertıg<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet / als wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_609_r1l12">Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dıenſt vnd wolgefallen etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_609_r1l13"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> Jn <expan>vıgı<ex>lia</ex></expan> <expan>Annu<ex>n</ex>cıac<ex>i</ex>o<ex>n</ex>ıs</expan> marıe <expan>vırg<ex>in</ex>ıs</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_609" id="303v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Herczog <expan>Wilhelm<ex>m</ex></expan> von Peyern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> nehst
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> haben als von des
                            <expan>Wernh<ex>er</ex></expan> Newmeyrs <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        etc., also <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> wir zu
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Erlpek<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem wir befolhen haben,
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu erczeln, wie sich
                                <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan> sache
                            <expan>ergang<ex>en</ex></expan> haben; und
                            <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
                        mit fleisz, was <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> in <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> sachen
                        zu disem mal von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewr gnade werbe, daz ir in <add>umb
                                    <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan></add> darinn
                            <expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan>, im des <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        gelawben und <expan>günstikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> von
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> darumb <expan>fertig<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        wellet, als wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> etc. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dienst und wolgefallen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in <expan>vigi<ex>lia</ex></expan>
<expan>annu<ex>n</ex>ciac<ex>i</ex>o<ex>n</ex>is</expan> Marie
                                <expan>virg<ex>in</ex>is</expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
